				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Thu%E1%BB%B7-huy%E1%BB%87n-Th%C3%B4i-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%ADu-%C3%B4ng-cao-trai-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-jee9SU4z1mg8j-OgwK2PPA">Bạch Thuỷ huyện Thôi thiếu phủ thập cửu ông cao trai tam thập vận - 白水縣崔少府十九翁高齋三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-L%E1%BB%8Bch-tam-ni%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF-th%C3%A0nh-ph%C3%B3ng-thuy%E1%BB%81n-xu%E1%BA%A5t-C%C3%B9-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-gi%C3%A1p-c%E1%BB%ADu-c%C6%B0-Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A7-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch/poem-FdJ4yvYyTSKfMStGhGDgGg">Đại Lịch tam niên xuân Bạch Đế thành phóng thuyền xuất Cù Đường giáp, cửu cư Quỳ Phủ tương thích Giang Lăng phiêu bạc, hữu thi phàm tứ thập vận - 大歷三年春白帝城放船出瞿唐峽久居夔府將適江陵漂泊有詩凡四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Hi%E1%BB%87n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/%C4%90%C3%A1p-t%C4%83ng-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-N3WfviYbvb0sUA5eFPjXhQ">Đáp tăng vấn - 答僧問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hi%E1%BB%87n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-3uiK-x6cVnkIzCo2phFuMg">Hiện Quang thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Linh-V%E1%BA%ADn/%C4%90%C4%83ng-giang-trung-C%C3%B4-D%E1%BB%B1/poem-69yD_2n8HgjW4B5POyZXsg">Đăng giang trung Cô Dự - 登江中孤嶼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Linh-V%E1%BA%ADn/author-7k3dwdcuJKTWbJGjPLm2kg">Tạ Linh Vận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-thi/poem-Cepi8wytvmdd_alLJQy7qg">Độc thi - 讀詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Nh%C3%A0n-t%C3%ACnh-ph%C3%BA/poem-SfJjdY1BShl5c2Q2RpHH7g">Nhàn tình phú - 閑情賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%E1%BB%81-T%C6%B0/Qu%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2m-ca-t%E1%BA%B7ng-H%E1%BB%93-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i/poem-tNU-HgaLeDQ-5DB4NKHUgQ">Quế Lâm ca tặng Hồ tú tài - 桂林歌贈胡秀才</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%E1%BB%81-T%C6%B0/author-iORDIpdUm3k9JfYMnUFi-Q">Yết Hề Tư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-chi%E1%BA%BFn-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca/poem-r-0sKzn4t1sF64MC4QGgRg">Thạch tướng quân chiến trường ca - 石將軍戰場歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QwR8mfkWimm7tarlC84k4w">Lý Mộng Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quan-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-Gi%E1%BA%A3i-Qu%C3%A2n-ti%E1%BB%81n-b%E1%BB%91i-t%E1%BB%B1-Y-L%C3%AA-lai-th%C6%B0-ph%C3%BA-th%E1%BB%AD-kh%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-k%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-LqjEJrK0xaqzvlQR8qVo7A">Tương xuất Ngọc Quan đắc Giải Quân tiền bối tự Y Lê lai thư phú thử khước ký kỳ 1 - 將出玉關得嶰筠前輩自伊犁來書賦此卻寄其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/author-JAv5RkZakjKTfe65gwrmsQ">Lâm Tắc Từ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%8Bch/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-thi-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-21/poem-J7bwDzXuxopaDal06UW6sw">Vịnh hoài thi (ngũ ngôn) kỳ 21 - 詠懷詩（五言）其二十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%8Bch/author-iqPFGu2O2IWkMRslgHjtDw">Nguyễn Tịch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
